To create a new gtk app project, simply use dotnet new templating engine:
dotnet new --install GtkSharp.Template.CSharp
dotnet new --uninstall GtkSharp.Template.CSharp

dotnet new gtkapp -o ModelViewPresenter
dotnet build
dotnet run